cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use DiscoSights in research, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: DiscoSights
abstract: "A configurable county similarity and correlation explorer for US policy research. Enables module-based peer county discovery using Euclidean distance in user-defined variable subspaces across 20 socioeconomic datasets. Includes gravity model calibration, IRS migration validation, dynamic terrain visualization, and within-group correlation analysis."
authors:
